{
  "texts": [
    "The ComBat method is employed to minimize these batch effects to improve data quality and accuracy.",
    "However, there are certain limitations associated with this batch correction method.",
    "First, ComBat is effective only with specific data types such as transcriptomics data, which includes data generated from technologies like microarrays and RNA sequencing (RNAseq).",
    "Secondly, there should be at least one dataset that includes both case and control groups within the same dataset, or else ComBat will not be applicable.",
    "By implementing PandaOmics in the drug discovery process, the Insilico Medicine company has already showcased successful instances and achieved advancements up to preclinical studies within a period of ~ 18 months (Pun et al. 2022; Ren et al. 2023)."
  ]
}